79e7f790cb2d57a722da85c9c23f0/TidalVST.scd#L91-L97\r\n\r\nFor accurate timing, the MIDI messages should be scheduled as OSC bundles instead. For example:\r\n\r\n```\r\n~dirt.server.makeBundle(latency, {\r\n    instruments[vstName].midi.noteOn(0, note, velocity);\r\n});\r\n\r\n~dirt.server.makeBundle(sustain + latency, {\r\n    instruments[vstName].midi.noteOff(0, note, velocity);\r\n});\r\n```", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/thgrund/TidalVST/issues/4/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/thgrund/TidalVST/issues/4/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}]}